but they're maxed out.

760
00:34:39.378 --> 00:34:41.430
I know. I know. And that's...
that's why I didn't call you.

761
00:34:41.513 --> 00:34:43.165
because I-I know.
and I-I'm working on it.

762
00:34:43.248 --> 00:34:44.799
Oh. thank you.

763
00:34:44.882 --> 00:34:47.319
What is that?

764
