And how do you know?

776
00:35:15.314 --> 00:35:17.216
'Cause I'm about
to take it there.

777
00:35:21.019 --> 00:35:23.289
-Uh-huh. What the... Oh!
-Come here.

778
00:35:23.389 --> 00:35:24.807
