we're pretty fucking ready.

801
00:36:11.970 --> 00:36:13.522
All right.
First thing Monday. my office.

802
00:36:13.605 --> 00:36:15.974
No. my office. and bring
all your little partners

803
00:36:16.074 --> 00:36:18.757
