little typewriters and shit.

804
00:36:18.844 --> 00:36:20.663
the whole shiteree.
I don't give a damn.

805
00:36:20.746 --> 00:36:22.814
-Fine. Fine.
-All right?

806
00:36:24.416 --> 00:36:27.570
