1109
00:49:35.573 --> 00:49:38.876
♪ Time and time again ♪

1110
00:49:40.745 --> 00:49:45.083
♪ Never knowing
if I'll sink or if I'll swim ♪

1111
00:49:45.183 --> 00:49:47.835
[sobbing]

1112
00:49:47.918 --> 00:49:52.257
♪ All the lights are low ♪

1113
00:49:52.390 --> 00:49:54.159
