1114
00:49:54.259 --> 00:49:58.163
♪ And the air is cold ♪

1115
00:50:00.431 --> 00:50:02.767
♪ Everything I know ♪

1116
00:50:02.867 --> 00:50:06.171
♪ Is touch-and-go ♪

1117
00:50:08.206 --> 00:50:12.277
♪ Tell me. are these ghosts? ♪

1118
00:50:12.410 --> 00:50:15.563
